  "body": "### Description\r\nAdd switch to enable / disable `Who holds` option:\r\n\r\n![Screenshot 2022-11-29 at 13 45 51](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97019400/204532821-f8dfeea4-6cab-4f09-b510-fbafc353f5b0.png)\r\n\r\nAnd, when disabled:\r\n![Screenshot 2022-12-12 at 13 58 21](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97019400/207050986-40816dd9-c133-49e9-903e-a6bbe666e30b.png)\r\n\r\nAnd if it is disabled, the `Is allowed to` and `In` sections behavior will be the following:\r\n![Screenshot 2023-01-11 at 10 16 04](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97019400/211766157-78860f19-5e1e-4e3b-bdbf-9233b98080c5.png)\r\n\r\nThe design here: \r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/17fc13UBFvInrLgNUKJJg5/Kuba%E2%8E%9CDesktop?node-id=2934%3A480020&t=tBWgno87dJA66V1N-0",
